1  Nejoki Yesu ilooiteng'eni lenyena, “Meeta nchere mepuonu ntemat e nkarrueisho; kake ee kake aiyia ilo laa ninye eimu! 
2  Enaikash te neenikini ninye osoit oiutuutishoreki emurt nenang'akini atua enaiposha, alang te neitapong'oo nabo e kuna kutiti. 
3   Entodol ate; te neitarruoo olalashe lino, irorie, ore pee eirridua, tapalaki; 
4  naa te nikinyala nabo, olong kat naapishana, nikingil kat naapishana ajoki, ‘airridua’, nipalaki ake.”

Enkirukoto


5  Nejoki ilooiteng'eni, “Olaitoriani, toponiki iyiook enkirukoto!” 
6  Nejoki Olaitoriani, “Te naa iatata napaji enkirukoto naba anaa enkantererai e karadali, indimidimi aatiaaki ele ng'aboli, ‘Tadotunye, tuunokinoyu enaiposha.’ nening intae.

Enaishiaakino olaisiaayiani


7  “Keetae obo linyi oata osinka oturisho aashu oloirritisho, ojoki te nelotu eing'uaa enkurma, ‘Wou nabo kata totona tadaayu?’ 
8  Anaa keng'as ake ajoki, ‘Tang'asa taa ntobirakaki endaa, nirretena nikiyaki, ore aidipa atadaayu naokisho; nilo sii iyie adaa niokisho?’ 
9  Ijojo pasa keisho ilo sinka enashe enkaraki nataasa enaitanapaki? 
10  Neijia itiuu sii intae, ore pee ndipidipi aataas inaaitanapaki intae pooki, entejo, ‘Mikira sinkan le tipat; kitaasa ake iyiook enaishiaakino nikiaas.’

Iltung'ana tomon ooishiunye Yesu


11  Neaku ore te nkoitoi elo Yerusalem neim erishata e Samaria o Galilaya. 
12  Ore ejing enkang nabo, nenang'are ltung'ana tomon ooata enkeeya oo lbolot neitashe ninche te nelakua 
13  nebuaku aajo, “Olaitoriani, Yesu, ing'urrie iyiook.” 
14   Ore pee edol ninye ninche nejoki, “Enchom entoduaai ate too lapolosak.” Ore epuoito neishiu nesika. 
15  Ore pee edol obo lenye ajo eishiunyeki, neshukunye eisisita Enkai to ltoilo sapuk; 
16  neirrabalakino enkop too nkejek e Yesu, ejoki ashe. Naa Osamariyiai ninye. 
17  Nejoki Yesu, “Ai mme tomon duoo ilaishiunye metisikata? Koree lkulikae pokira ooudo? 
18  Kaji etiu pee eitu etumi obo oshukunye aisho Enkai enashe meteleku ele leeiking'a?” 
19  Nejoki ninye ilo, “Inyo shomo; kintajewuo enkirukoto ino.”

Elotunoto e nkitoria e Nkai

(Mat 
24  .
23  -
28  ,
37  -
41  )


20  Ore pee eikilikuan Ilfarisayo enkata nalotu enkitoria e Nkai, newaliki ajoki ninche, “Melotu enkitoria e Nkai too lmonek oolioo; 
21  nemeyookini aajo, ‘She, nena natii ene!’ aashu ‘Neidia!’ amu ng'ura, etii enkitoria e Nkai atua intae.”


22  Nejoki Yesu ilooiteng'eni lenyena, “Kepuonu inkolong'i naa ing'uarring'uarra te ni idolidolo enkolong nabo e Nkerai e Tung'ani, nimidolidolo. 
23  Naa kejokini intae, ‘Ng'ura ende!’ aashu, ‘Ng'ura ene!’ Emipuo ake emirubare. 
24  Amu ore enatiu enkiwuang'ata naimerlelu neitawang embata nabo e shumata o metabaiki enkae, neijia etiu Enkerai e Tung'ani te ina olong enye. 
25  Kake ore eitu ebau ine eng'asi ake aainyal too nkumok neany iltung'ana le na kata. 
26   Ore anaa enatiu apa too nkolong'i e Noah, neijia etiu too nkolong'i e Nkerai e Tung'ani. 
27   Kedaai apa, neokishoi, neyamishoi, neishoori meyami, o meeu ina olong natijing'a Noa atua emeli, nelotu oloirrag le nkare nemut ninche pooki. 
28   Neijia sii apa etiu too nkolong'i e Lot aa, kedaae apa, neokishoi, neinyiang'ishoi, nemirishoi, neunishoi, neshetishoi, 
29  kake ore ake ina olong natupukuo Lot aing'uaa Sodom neshau enkima oo soito le nkima eing'uaa shumata neidaikie ninche pooki. 
30  Neijia sii etiu ina olong naibalunyeki Enkerai e Tung'ani.


31   Ore te ina olong, inchoo ilo otii shumata enkaji, oata ntokitin ti atua, milotu ake ajo aya; ore sii ilo otii enkurma mirrinyo ake. 
32   Entadamu enkitok e Lot. 
33   Ore pooki ng'ae ojo agolie enkishui enye neiminie, kake ore pooki oiturraa enkishui enye neitopoki. 
34  Ajoki intae, “Ore te ina kewarie keirrag ltung'ana aare erruat nabo; neyai obo, neing'uari olikae. 
35  Neiutuutisho nkituaak are te nebo to soit obo; neyai nabo neing'uari enkae. 
36  [Netii ltung'ana aare enkurma; neyae obo neing'uari olikae.”] 
37  Nejoki ninche ninye, “Olaitoriani, ae ti aji?” Nejoki, “Enetii empopok, eiturrurrokino lmotonyi.”

